Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: party food planner
des: Party Food Planner provides users the ability to select food options for a party. Users can select alcoholic/non-alcoholic Beverages, veg/non-veg Appetizers, veg/non-veg Main Course and sweet/sour Desserts from multiple cuisines (Indian/American). Party food planner then provides the options based on user's selected preferences.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
